result.description:
The implementation phase of the GEPs will commence in the second half of the Action. It will be required:
for those partner institutes that don’t have GEPs to put them in place and;
•	for those partner institutes that already have GEPs to revise them.

The task leader will:
collect institutional practices and national legislations from participants regarding support systems for child-care and elder-care, and family-friendly working conditions;
compare the practices, wherein national and cultural difference will be depicted;
provide an inventory of practices and recommendations for employers and employees to be circulated among partners and other linked institutions.
